  "title": "Sales Advisors (Luxury brands) X 20 @ Central/East | Fast Hiring | $$$",
  "description": "<p><strong>Sales Advisors (Luxury brands) X 20 @ Central/East | Fast Hiring | $$$</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>📍 <strong>Location:</strong>Central/East Region</p>\n<p>💼 <strong>Job Type:</strong>Full-Time</p>\n<p>🕒 <strong>Timing/Shifts:</strong>Retail Hours, Roster-Based / 44 hours work week</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Are you passionate about luxury fashion, personalized styling, and creating unforgettable client experiences?</strong></p>\n<p>Join <strong>US</strong> and be part of an iconic global brand that defines modern elegance and sophistication.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>✨ <strong>What You’ll Do</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Deliver a world-class luxury shopping experience to every client.</li>\n  <li>Provide expert styling advice and personalized product recommendations.</li>\n  <li>Build and nurture long-term client relationships through clienteling and follow-ups.</li>\n  <li>Consistently achieve or exceed individual and boutique sales targets.</li>\n  <li>Uphold brand image and luxury service standards at all times.</li>\n  <li>Support visual merchandising, stock management, and store events.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>🌟 <strong>What We’re Looking For</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Experience in <strong>luxury or premium fashion retail</strong> preferred.</li>\n  <li>Sales-driven, confident, and proactive in achieving targets.</li>\n  <li>Impeccable grooming and professionalism.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>📩 Interested? Apply Now!</strong></p>\n<p>Send your resume to: <a href=\"mailto:Vanessa.chua@crew.sg\">Vanessa.chua@crew.sg</a></p>\n<p>Please include your <strong>availability</strong>, <strong>notice period</strong>, <strong>expected salary and a professional photo of yourself</strong>.</p>\n<p><em>* Only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</em></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Vanessa Chua Peng Teng (R25158315)</strong></p>\n<p>Associate Consultant</p>\n<p>HRnet Ventures Pte Ltd - CREW by HRnet</p>\n<p><strong>E.A. 24C2435</strong></p>",
